        } catch (FileNotFoundException fnfe) {
            System.out.println("Was not able to locate testfile.txt.");
        }
    }
}

In this code, the PrintWriter is opened before the while loop. Inside the loop, each line of the input file is printed with its line number and also written to the output file. After the while loop, the PrintWriter is closed. This way, all lines from the input file are written to the output file with their line numbers.

